### Warehouse Config Service - REST Client examples
# Variables
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT
@direct = http://localhost:3020
@gateway = http://localhost:8000/warehouse-config

### Health (direct)
GET {{@direct}}/health

### Health (via Kong)
GET {{@gateway}}/health

### Vehicles: create
POST {{@gateway}}/api/v1/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouse_id": "REPLACE-WAREHOUSE-UUID",
  "vehicle_code": "V-DEV-001",
  "vehicle_type": "VAN",
  "license_plate": "B-01-DEV",
  "max_weight_kg": 1200
}

### Vehicles: get by id
GET {{@gateway}}/api/v1/vehicles/REPLACE-VEHICLE-UUID
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}

### Vehicles: list (with pagination)
GET {{@gateway}}/api/v1/vehicles?page=1&limit=20&sortBy=vehicle_code&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}

### Delivery zones: create
POST {{@gateway}}/api/v1/delivery-zones
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouse_id": "REPLACE-WAREHOUSE-UUID",
  "zone_code": "DZ-LOCAL-01",
  "zone_name": "Bucuresti",
  "zone_type": "LOCAL",
  "regions": ["Bucuresti"]
}

### Delivery zones: list for warehouse
GET {{@gateway}}/api/v1/warehouses/REPLACE-WAREHOUSE-UUID/delivery-zones
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}

### Delivery zones: list for warehouse (with pagination)
GET {{@gateway}}/api/v1/warehouses/REPLACE-WAREHOUSE-UUID/delivery-zones?page=1&limit=10&sortBy=zone_code&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}

### Delivery zone: upsert carrier availability
POST {{@gateway}}/api/v1/delivery-zones/REPLACE-ZONE-UUID/carriers
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrier_id": "REPLACE-CARRIER-UUID",
  "priority": 1,
  "estimated_delivery_days": 1,
  "is_available": true
}

### Workflow: create state
POST {{@gateway}}/api/v1/workflow/states
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state_code": "TEST_STATE",
  "state_name": "Test State",
  "state_category": "QC"
}

### Workflow: list states for a warehouse
GET {{@gateway}}/api/v1/warehouses/REPLACE-WAREHOUSE-UUID/workflow/states
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}

### Warehouse settings: create
POST {{@gateway}}/api/v1/warehouse-settings
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouse_id": "REPLACE-WAREHOUSE-UUID",
  "setting_category": "INVENTORY",
  "setting_key": "putaway.strategy",
  "setting_value": "fixed-location",
  "setting_type": "STRING",
  "validation_rules": { "enum": ["fixed-location","closest-fit","randomized"] }
}

### Warehouse settings: list (by category, with pagination)
GET {{@gateway}}/api/v1/warehouses/REPLACE-WAREHOUSE-UUID/settings?category=INVENTORY&page=1&limit=20&sortBy=setting_category&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{@token}}
